Key F9 A M Nop
Key F10 A M Nop
Key F11 A M Nop
Key F12 A M Nop

AddToFunc Naked
+ I Style (NoTitle)
+ I Style (NoBorder)
Key b A 4 Naked

Key r A 4 Restart

AddToFunc Eterm1
+ I Maximize true 100 80
AddToFunc Eterm2
+ I Maximize true 100 80
+ I Move 0 -0
AddToFunc Eterm3
+ I Maximize true 96 80
+ I Move 2 0
AddToFunc Eterm4
+ I Maximize true 96 20
+ I Move 2 -2
Key 1 A 4 Eterm1
Key 2 A 4 Eterm2
Key 3 A 4 Eterm3
Key 4 A 4 Eterm4
